# Manufacturing Process

## Equipment
- Double boiler
- Mixer
- Silicone molds

## Steps
1. Heat fatty phase to 70°C
2. Add surfactants gradually
3. Mix until uniform paste
4. Cool to 45°C
5. Add fragrance/actives
6. Mold and press

## Common Issues
- Soft bars → Increase fatty alcohols
- Crumbling → Add more binder (BTMS)
